text: I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! returned for its tenth series on 14 November 2010. It ran for 3 weeks. Ant & Dec returned as the presenters for the main show. Its spin off show Get Me out of Here... Now returned with Caroline Flack and Joe Swash as main presenters. On 4 December 2010, singer Stacey Solomon won the show.
